[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0459","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0459.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0273","title":"Sun Solaris 2.5.1 Telnet 控制字符拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 2.5.1 Telnet 服务存在控制字符处理缺陷，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向目标系统的 telnet 端口发送 ^D（Ctrl+D）控制字符，导致 telnet 守护进程崩溃或进入异常状态，从而造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 2.5.1 操作系统，攻击利用难度低，无需特殊权限即可触发，属于典型的拒绝服务漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0273"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.973","remediation":"升级至 Oracle Solaris 11 或更高版本，并停止使用 telnet 服务；在 inetd.conf 中注释 telnet 行（或执行 svcadm disable telnet），改用 SSH 作为远程管理协议。若必须运行旧版系统，限制 telnet 服务的源 IP 访问并部署入侵检测规则监控异常 ^D 字符序列。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0273","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0273.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0273","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0273.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0273.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0273.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2mh6-5954-wmgr/GHSA-2mh6-5954-wmgr.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/sunkill.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0273.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82086/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0459.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0465","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0465.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0279","title":"Excite Excite for Web Servers 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Excite for Web Servers（EWS）存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向服务提交包含 shell 元字符（如管道符、分号）的恶意请求，在服务进程中执行任意操作系统命令。该漏洞源于 EWS 对用户输入过滤不严，未正确处理 shell 特殊字符，导致攻击者可远程控制目标服务器。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0279"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:03.717","remediation":"Excite for Web Servers (EWS) 已停止维护多年，无官方补丁。建议立即迁移至现代 Web 服务器（如 Apache/Nginx）替代 EWS。如无法立即迁移，在反向代理层过滤用户输入中的 shell 元字符（; | ` $ &）、严格限制 CGI 参数、并对 Web 服务目录实施最小权限访问控制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0279","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0279.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0279","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0279.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0279.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0279.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qrgq-23c9-3qrw/GHSA-qrgq-23c9-3qrw.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/E/ews.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0279.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0465.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0473","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0473.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0284","title":"多款邮件服务器 SMTP HELO 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Alt-N MDaemon Server 2.71 SP1 及 Microsoft Exchange Server 4.0/5.0 等邮件服务器的 SMTP HELO 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标服务器的 25 端口发送超长 HELO 参数，触发缓冲区溢出，导致目标邮件服务程序崩溃造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Ipswitch、MDaemon、Exchange 等多款 NT 平台邮件服务器，属于经典的早期 SMTP 协议栈溢出攻击案例。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0284"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.237","remediation":"升级 Alt-N MDaemon 至 3.0 及以上版本，或升级 Microsoft Exchange Server 至 5.5 及以上版本并安装最新 Service Pack；在 SMTP 服务层对 HELO/EHLO 参数做长度限制与输入校验；在防火墙限制 SMTP（25端口）只对信任来源开放作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0284","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/23113","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0284.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0284","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0284.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0284.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0284.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v64w-xq9r-xp4x/GHSA-v64w-xq9r-xp4x.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/M/mdaemon.nasl","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/slmail_helo.nasl","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0284.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0473.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0473.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0473.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0487","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0487.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0293","title":"Cisco IOS AAA认证远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 系统的 AAA（认证、授权、审计）认证模块存在授权绕过漏洞，远程攻击者可在未获得合法凭据的情况下绕过认证机制，直接执行任意命令。该漏洞影响多款 Cisco 路由器及交换机设备，攻击者利用该漏洞可完全控制目标设备，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。目前建议用户升级至修复版本或配置严格的访问控制列表进行缓解。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0293"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:05.380","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至修复该漏洞的版本（如 11.x 及以上已打补丁版本），启用 `aaa new-model` 并配置 TACACS+ 或 RADIUS 服务器进行认证授权，避免仅依赖本地 enable 密码。在 `aaa authentication` 和 `aaa authorization` 命令中指定 `group tacacs+` 作为首选方法，禁止未认证用户通过 AAA 接口执行命令。如无法升级，在受控接口上配置 ACL 限制仅允许可信管理源 IP 访问设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0293","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0293.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0293","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0293.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0293.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0293.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-wmmp-2f22-959m/GHSA-wmmp-2f22-959m.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2007/CVE-2007-4632.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82266/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0293.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0487.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0547","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0547.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0331","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.0 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.0/4.0.1 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可构造特制网页或 URL，诱使用户访问后触发缓冲区溢出，导致浏览器崩溃或执行任意代码。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台上 IE 4.0 及 4.0.1 版本，攻击复杂度低且无需认证，仅需用户交互即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0331"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:10.197","remediation":"立即升级至 Internet Explorer 5.01 及以上版本，Microsoft 已在 IE 5.0 中修复此缓冲区溢出漏洞。对于当前仍在使用的旧系统，应停止使用 IE 4.0 并迁移至 Microsoft Edge 或 Chrome 等受支持的现代浏览器。如无法升级浏览器，可通过防火墙限制受感染主机对外部恶意服务器的 80/443 端口访问作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0331","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0331.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0331","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0331.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0331.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/057c97aa60eb958a2d272c7164e35c156db63b6c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pjph-v9v4-hggg/GHSA-pjph-v9v4-hggg.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0331.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0547.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0547.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0560","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0560.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0341","title":"Debian Linux deliver 邮件程序本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Debian Linux 系统中的 mail 程序 \"deliver\" 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞通过精心构造的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取系统 root 权限。该漏洞需攻击者拥有本地访问权限，危害等级高，影响 Debian Linux 系统。建议及时安装厂商发布的安全补丁进行修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0341"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.357","remediation":"升级 Linux 发行版至至少 Debian 3.0（Woody）以上版本，该版本已移除有漏洞的 deliver 程序，改用更安全的邮件传输代理。如因特殊原因仍使用 deliver，立即将其 SUID 权限移除（chmod u-s /usr/bin/deliver），并迁移至 exim 或 postfix 等现代 MTA。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0341"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0560.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0242","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0242.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0107","title":"Apache HTTP Server 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Apache 1.2.5 及更早版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送大量包含大量 `/` 字符的恶意 GET 请求触发此漏洞，导致 Apache 服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Apache 1.2.5 及之前所有版本，攻击无需身份认证，利用难度较低，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0107"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-12-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.150","remediation":"建议升级至 Apache 1.3.0 及以上版本，该版本已修复超大 GET 请求导致的缓冲区溢出。如无法升级，可在反向代理层（如 Nginx）限制单个 URI 长度不超过 4096 字节，并在 Web 应用防火墙中配置请求速率限制以缓解 DDoS 风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0107","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20558","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0107.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0107.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0107","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0107.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0107.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0107.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qq9g-rvjp-rm4j/GHSA-qq9g-rvjp-rm4j.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0107.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0242.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0048","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0048.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0015","title":"Microsoft Windows TCP/IP 分片重组拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Teardrop 拒绝服务漏洞利用 IP 分片重组机制的缺陷，攻击者向目标系统发送含有重叠偏移量的特制 IP 分片数据包，导致系统在重组时发生内存损坏而崩溃或重启。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 10.34、Windows 95/NT 3.5.1/NT 4.0 及后续 Service Pack 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程触发，造成目标服务中断。此漏洞为早期经典的 DoS 攻击类型，已被公开的利用代码广泛使用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0015"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:21.280","remediation":"对于 Windows 95/NT 4.0 及更早版本，该漏洞官方补丁已停止支持，最终修复方案是升级到 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2016 以上版本。对于 HP-UX 10.34，应升级到 HP-UX 11i v3 并安装最新补丁包。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙上配置 ACL 规则丢弃非法 IP 分片包（如碎片偏移量重叠的数据包），并在受影响主机上禁用非必要的网络服务以减少攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A5579","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19103","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0015.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0015","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0015.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0015.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0015.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xj3h-gcxj-7pw6/GHSA-xj3h-gcxj-7pw6.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/franckferman/Floodles/blob/144ec41e2f9052ac35701c26fe9e1fb081c44ef6/modules/ip_frag.py","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/T/teardrop.nasl","https://github.com/brevityinmotion/straylight/blob/3a51188edc3c08c6801402d81188f060cccd8d03/notebooks/Detectify-Learning.ipynb"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0048.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0053","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0053.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0015","title":"Microsoft Windows TCP Teardrop 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Teardrop（泪滴）攻击是一种IP分片重组拒绝服务漏洞，攻击者通过向目标系统发送精心构造的、分片偏移量存在重叠的恶意IP数据包，导致目标系统在重组分片时触发内存计算错误，进而造成系统崩溃或重启。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Windows 95/NT 3.51/NT 4.0 及 HP-UX 10.34 等操作系统，远程攻击者无需认证即可利用此漏洞，但需能够向目标发送IP数据包。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0015"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:21.280","remediation":"立即安装微软 MS98-001 安全更新（KB168747）以修复 TCP/IP 分片重组缺陷；对于已停止支持的 Windows 95/NT 4.0，建议升级至 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2016 以上版本；可在网络边界防火墙配置规则丢弃异常偏移的 IP 分片包作为临时缓解措施。针对 HP-UX 10.34，请升级至 HP-UX 11.0 以上版本或安装对应补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A5579","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19103"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0053.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0033","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0033.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0004","title":"多种邮件客户端 MIME 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"多种邮件客户端在处理带有超长文件名的邮件附件或MIME消息时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可向受影响系统发送特制的邮件消息，触发缓冲区溢出，导致邮件客户端崩溃或潜在的任意代码执行。该漏洞影响Sun Solaris dtmail（mailtool）以及Microsoft Outlook 98和Outlook Express 4.x等多个平台的邮件客户端程序，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程触发。厂商已发布相应安全补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0004"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-12-16","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"Outlook 98 用户应从 Office Update 下载并安装补丁（https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?FamilyID=5D865C89-8BAC-42C0-AFCD-53E74E152234）。Outlook Express 4.x 用户应先升级至 Internet Explorer 4.01 SP1，再安装 Outlook Express 更新补丁。Solaris dtmail 用户应安装 Sun 官方补丁（Solaris 7: patch 106876-01; Solaris 2.6: patch 105779-01）。如无法升级，建议禁用受影响邮件客户端或改用其他邮件客户端处理 MIME 邮件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-008","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0004"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0033.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0237","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0237.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0104","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/NT 4.0 Teardrop IP 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Teardrop-2 是 Teardrop IP 拒绝服务攻击的变种，影响 Microsoft Windows 95 和 Windows NT 4.0 操作系统。攻击者通过向目标系统发送特制的 IP 分片数据包，利用 IP 协议栈在分片重组时对偏移量字段处理不当的缺陷，使目标系统消耗大量资源处理畸形分片，最终导致系统崩溃或蓝屏，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞无需认证即可远程触发，攻击门槛低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0104"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-12-16","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本（这些旧版系统已停止支持）。无法升级时，在边界防火墙上过滤 IP 分片包（设置最小分片大小为 552 字节），或在主机上禁用受影响协议的 IP 分片功能，可有效缓解该漏洞利用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/80175","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A5743"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0237.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0415","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0415.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0230","title":"Cisco 7xx 路由器 Telnet 服务缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Cisco 7xx 系列路由器 telnet 服务存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标设备的 telnet 端口发送特制的超长请求，触发缓冲区溢出，可能导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 Cisco 7xx 系列路由器，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。厂商已发布固件更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0230"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-12-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.653","remediation":"升级 Cisco 7xx 系列路由器 IOS 至不受 1999 年 telnet 缓冲区溢出漏洞影响的版本（如 11.3 以上），或在全局配置模式下使用 `access-class` 限制 telnet 访问源地址，或禁用 telnet 服务改用 SSH 协议。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1102","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0230.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0230","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0230.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0230.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0230.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9hrh-6m37-36f5/GHSA-9hrh-6m37-36f5.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0230.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0415.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0063","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0063.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0017","title":"Caldera OpenLinux FTP PORT 命令远程端口转发漏洞","description":"FTP 协议存在 FTP 反弹（FTP Bounce）漏洞，攻击者可通过 FTP 客户端的 PORT 命令指示 FTP 服务器向任意第三方主机的任意端口发起连接，从而利用该 FTP 服务器作为跳板绕过网络访问控制，实现对内网或其他受限网络的端口扫描与间接攻击。该漏洞影响多数支持主动模式（PORT 命令）的 FTP 服务器软件，攻击条件低，仅需能够与 FTP 服务器建立控制连接。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0017"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-12-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:21.560","remediation":"升级 FTP 服务器软件至支持 PORT 命令限制的版本（如 wu-ftpd 2.6.1+、vsftpd 2.0.1+），并启用第三方地址连接检查功能；在防火墙层面限制 FTP 服务器主动发起的出站连接，仅允许到客户端 IP 的 1024 以上端口；配置 FTP 服务端禁止 PORT 命令指向非客户端 IP 地址。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0017"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0063.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0059","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0059.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0018","title":"IBM AIX、SCO Unixware、SGI IRIX、Sun Solaris statd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"statd 服务存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制 RPC 请求，触发 statd 守护进程中的缓冲区溢出，进而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 3.2/4.1、SCO Unixware 7.1.1、SGI IRIX 5.3 及 Sun Solaris 2.5.1 等多款 Unix 操作系统，利用方式为网络远程攻击，无需身份认证。CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0018"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-12-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:21.700","remediation":"立即安装各厂商提供的 rpc.statd 补丁包：Sun Solaris 2.5.1 安装 Sun 补丁 ID 105402-02 或更新版本；IBM AIX 4.1 安装 APAR IX64628；SGI IRIX 5.3 安装 SGI 安全补丁 19970801-01-P。如系统已停止维护，应升级到受支持的操作系统版本。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上禁止外部访问 portmap（TCP/UDP 111）和 rpc.statd 使用的动态端口（通常为 32771/4045），或停止 rpc.statd 服务（`/etc/init.d/rpc.statd stop`）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/127","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19104","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0018.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0018","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0018.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0018.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2p8f-w9gg-hwrc/GHSA-2p8f-w9gg-hwrc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/rpc_statd.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0059.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0376","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0376.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0193","title":"3Com 路由器 TCP 零长选项拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Ascend 与 3Com 路由器在处理特殊构造的 TCP 数据包时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标路由器发送包含零长度 TCP 选项（Zero Length TCP Option）的恶意数据包，触发设备处理异常导致路由器强制重启或崩溃。该漏洞影响 Ascend R 4.5 Ci12 及部分 3Com 路由器版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。目前厂商已发布固件更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0193"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:52.973","remediation":"建议升级 Ascend Router 固件至 4.5 Ci12 之后的修复版本，或升级 3Com 路由器至厂商发布的修补固件。若暂时无法升级，可在边界防火墙配置规则丢弃 TCP 选项长度为 0 的异常数据包，同时启用 TCP 状态检测功能缓解攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0193","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20332","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0193.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0193","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0193.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0193.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0193.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5p2w-742f-cg75/GHSA-5p2w-742f-cg75.j